                    </div>
                    <span>If you only buy one baseball annual in 2005, this should be the one!  The Scouting notebook effectively humanizes the players to such a degree I felt like I could manage them to a pennant.  The writing style is crisp,and clean, easy to understand without becoming boringly predictable. This book makes for a fun companion for the 2005 season.</span>
                  
              
